description: **National Geographic Expeditions** is a community of climbers with a goal, that goal is to create a warm welcoming group of people who define RP in game, one that can be defined as National Geographic Expeditions. We aim to be successful and to strive toward a new era of Role Play in Roblox, We hope to reinforce this with our staff team and structure, So there you have a brief introduction, we were founded in 2017 and We welcome you to this community, have a nice day and Enjoy!
